You should define the command as follows:
NamedCommands.registerCommand("Your Command Name", Command)
PathPlanner Named Commands Documentation

Then, create an autonomous from the GUI. Click the + button in the top right corner, create a command, and make sure the name matches exactly with the one defined in the code. Press Enter to save the command to the GUI, allowing you to use it easily later.

Example:

image700×95 2.36 KB

Make sure to perform these definitions without creating any autonomous routines in the code.

image873×164 12.8 KB

Also, ensure that the autonomous command name matches exactly with the one in the GUI; otherwise, it will not work.
